getParent

public IHasID getParent()
Returns the parent containing this SemanticLabel instance.

Returns:
the parent containing this semantic label or null if the parent is not set

Note that this attribute is not a part of UBY-LMF. Therefore a semantic label may not have a parent set. In this case, this method returns null
